            <h2 id="sec0">Step 1: Order Your Parts</h2>

            <p> First, order all of your parts. We need all of the parts to create the entire setup. </p>
            <p> Next, depending on what CNC mill you have, and 3D printer you have, download the open-source
                software you need.
                The Ultimaker 2 uses <a href="https://ultimaker.com/en/products/cura-software">Cura</a>, and the
                OtherMill uses <a href="https://othermachine.co/otherplan/">Otherplan.</a>
                <br><br>
            </p>
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <!--<iframe width="854" height="480" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/vVoBc4fET_U?list=UUAmSyv1xQXCg9-jRaxpA4qg" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>-->
